Package: StopPropagHateR
Title: Hate Speech classification using Deep Learning to English and Portuguese
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Paula", "Fortuna", email = "paulatfortuna@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: In this package we provide deep learning models for hate speech classification (binary hate speech, sexism and racism). These were build using keras and allow text classification to Portuguese and English. 
Depends: R (>= 3.4.4)
Imports:
    downloader,
    keras,
    kerasR
